      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAPPY TOO YA (3) took a step up in grade and registered a respectable performance when he battled on well for fourth at Menangle last Saturday. Had been flying with four straight wins prior, three of them here. Should enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position so could return to the winners' list. JILLIBY FABIO (7) enjoyed the return to this venue when he came from this same barrier and scored by a head over this distance last week. That took his record here to three wins and two placings from six tries. Big chance. DOM TORETTO NZ (9) drew wide and was held up last start but recorded a string of wins and placings prior including a victory at Menangle. May need some luck from this draw but won the only time he raced here. LACEYS LAD NZ (8) could be close to another win after placing in his last three outings, two of them from this row.",
